{"tid":1215613,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"可能係對付狗隻最佳方法","createTime":"2019-06-13T07:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T17:08:18.000Z","uid":131079,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3780cf22055ac805421f0d6aa0583fde95999f91","tid":1215613,"uid":131079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:43:16.000Z","msg":"啲狗成身都係裝備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有防毒面具擋咗大部份氣體<br />\n有頭盔盾牌擋咗大部分物理攻擊<br />\n同佢硬碰硬好大機會輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係佢哋擋唔到聲波<br />\n一般嚟講5-10Hz對佢地內臟有影響<br />\n7Hz就最大影響<br />\n而20-30Hz就可以令佢地頭痛同肌肉疲勞(就算企喺度都好似行路咁，企足咁耐行足咁耐)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n60-90Hz對視力影響(當然要佢望住震源)<br />\n而15000-19000Hz可以針對住佢地隻耳<br />\n依家問題係搵唔到音響系統做到低同準確frequency(&lt;30)<br />\n歡迎各位巴絲入嚟諗下work唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c42259d494bc4dfa7a0f229f34763f15c66ed5","tid":1215613,"uid":251119,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:00:12.000Z","msg":"咁係咪要搵啲聾人示威者先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定你想tk哂全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"321d2cab3084824c4005570fc39416105b017a24","tid":1215613,"uid":131079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66c42259d494bc4dfa7a0f229f34763f15c66ed5","tid":1215613,"uid":251119,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:00:12.000Z","msg":"咁係咪要搵啲聾人示威者先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定你想tk哂全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"買定耳罩放喺物資站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同企喺震源後方"},{"pid":"d1380ea7615d0e71b153aeda2098e6db9e9e937a","tid":1215613,"uid":260004,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"66c42259d494bc4dfa7a0f229f347